Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.49,ZWOP,,0,0,0,,在不同寻常的漩涡之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.10,ZWOP,,0,0,0,,饱受自卑的煎熬 the way you want this
